    <abstract id="aspace_9d9301d8c706fe4cde655c743d64eafe">This collection contains a rolled engineer's blueprint of Ebbetts Field and 5 scrapbooks with newspaper and magazine pictures and articles about the Dodgers (1941-1957). Scrapbooks were compiled by Mr. Trapani, a Dodger fan, as a boy in Brooklyn.  The blueprint, dated 1954 (42½" x 35), was purchased by him at an auction for $15.</abstract>
